\begin_inset Text

\begin_layout Plain Layout

\series bold
\color blue
Reading project in Cosmology, General Relativity and Dark Matter
\begin_inset Newline linebreak
\end_inset


\size small
\color inherit
Dr.
 Subhadip Mitra, IIIT Hyderabad
\series default
\size default

\begin_inset Newline linebreak
\end_inset

A reading project in General Relativity, Cosmology and Dark Matter.
 I studied General Relativity and Cosmology following textbooks by Scott
 Dodelson, Bernard F.
 Schutz and James Hartle.
 This project helped me gain the understanding of the basics of Tensor algebra
 and calculus, General Relativity, Cosmology, and Dark Matter
